message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE. The paper proposes a novel deep learning architecture for cloze-style question answering, which is a task related to natural language processing and machine comprehension. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper uses bidirectional GRU networks, which are commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves decision making, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
